show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/kH9ath
show.description: Anika was auctioned like property—only to be claimed by ruthless billionaire Kabir, a man with secrets as dark as his past. What begins as a forced contract soon turns into a fiery war of emotions, power, and unexpected passion. Bought for a Billionaire is a stormy tale of possession, love, and the price of one woman's freedom. Watch Now!
